dc_title_s: Plan of the north part of the 11th ward, Camden, N.J. Cramer Hill
dc_description_s: This map embraces Lands lying between the Delaware River and the Pennsylvania Railroad, from Philadelphia to New York (Camden & Amboy). | |The Camden and suburban Trolly Cars run through this tract. Direct communication is made from foot of the 28th Street by two ferries, one to Otis Street, the other to Arch Street, Philadelphia.
